## TOPs Reality Capture OBJ Output

### Example HIP: 

* TOPs\_RealityCapture\_OBJ\_Output\_V001.hip

### Description:

Launch Reality Capture and output a wavefront obj mesh

The source photos and xmp metadata are loaded from:

* $HIP/images/\[\#\#\#\#\]/Reconstruction/Camera.NNNN.jpg  
* $HIP/images/\[\#\#\#\#\]/Reconstruction/Camera.NNNN.xmp

The region file is loaded from:

* $HIP\\metadata\\rec\_region.rcbox

The Reality Capture project file is opened:

* $HIP/images/\[\#\#\#\#\]/project\_xyz.rcproj

The Reality Capture project file is saved to:

* $HIP/images/\[\#\#\#\#\]/project\_obj.rcproj
